snippet.title: The Good Guy Inc
snippet.description:
Marvin Gaye what's going on everyone?!  My name is Terry, Founder & Creator of The Good Guy Inc.  On this channel I discuss a variety of different topics, many that deal with men, and I try to do so in an unbiased manner without pushing any hidden agendas.  My agendas are pretty obvious, and that is to help make sure each one of us can wake up a better self than the day previous.

As you will hear me say, I'm not a therapist or a psychologist or even a PHD graduate, I am just a regular dude talking about regular things.

So if this strikes your fancy, go hit that subscribe button and enjoy the wonderful ride full of cheesy jokes and at times thought provoking discussions!
